:

*Uradiš* li sve to što ti je rečeno, bićeš nagrađen. (If you *do* everything that was said to you, you will be rewarded.)

*Uradiš* li to što ti se traži, bit ćeš nagrađen. (If you *do* what is being asked of you, you will be rewarded.)

Sve što se od tebe traži možeš *uradiš*. (Everything that is being asked of you, you can *do*.)

Šta god da ti se traži, spremno *uradiš*. (Whatever is being asked of you, you *do* it willingly.)

Ako *uradiš* ono što ti se traži, svi će biti zadovoljni. (If you *do* what is being asked of you, everyone will be satisfied.)